      "message": "[warning] Line 86: The debounce key uses either peer or deviceId in the same namespace, so a peer id can collide with another notification\u0027s device id and make unrelated retry paths throttle each other. Use an unambiguous composite key that preserves the request scope, for example:\n```suggestion\n    const auto key \u003d deviceId.empty() ? \"peer:\" + peer : \"device:\" + peer + \u0027:\u0027 + deviceId;\n```",
